cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with language modeling for speech recognition. It could also belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with speech recognition. Additionally, it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves the use of neural networks for language modeling. Finally, it could belong to cs.SI (Signal Processing) as it involves processing of speech signals.
